18
00:03:10,759 --> 00:03:11,839
Actually, just now

19
00:03:48,360 --> 00:03:49,479
You're awake.

20
00:03:50,000 --> 00:03:51,399
You finally woke up.

21
00:03:53,559 --> 00:03:54,800
Do you know

22
