23
00:04:01,199 --> 00:04:02,000
Sima Kong.

24
00:04:16,079 --> 00:04:17,600
It's a relief that it's you this time.

25
00:04:17,760 --> 00:04:18,600
What?

26
00:04:19,799 --> 00:04:20,720
It's nothing.

27
00:04:21,720 --> 00:04:22,679
How is Lu Jiu?

28
00:04:22,799 --> 00:04:23,959
Thanks to your medicine,

29
