when you both smile,

37
00:04:39,000 --> 00:04:39,920
that's the best medicine.

38
00:04:40,000 --> 00:04:41,119
You did all this

39
00:04:41,320 --> 00:04:42,440
for us.

40
00:04:42,519 --> 00:04:44,600
Didn't Lu Jiu get poisoned to save me?

41
00:04:46,000 --> 00:04:47,000
Now we're even.

42
00:04:47,040 --> 00:04:48,160
How is this even?

43
00:04:48,200 --> 00:04:49,760
I checked your pulse.

44
00:04:50,040 --> 00:04:51,559
You've lost all your martial arts skills.

45
00:04:52,119 --> 00:04:53,160
On the journey to find the medicine,

46
00:04:53,200 --> 00:04:54,640
what exactly happened?

47
00:04:57,399 --> 00:04:59,359
I just returned something that didn't belong to me.

48
00:04:59,959 --> 00:05:01,720
To a place where it didn't belong to me.

49
00:05:03,359 --> 00:05:04,760
You don't need to worry about it so much.

50
00:05:05,000 --> 00:05:05,799
Now,

51
