It's a good thing for me too.

54
00:05:12,359 --> 00:05:13,359
A Tang Sect spy.

55
00:05:13,480 --> 00:05:14,600
There's nothing to hide.

56
00:05:15,040 --> 00:05:16,320
How did you know I was from the Tang Sect?

57
00:05:16,399 --> 00:05:17,320
Lie down quickly.

58
00:05:19,239 --> 00:05:20,440
Lu Jiu told me.

59
00:05:20,600 --> 00:05:21,720
