64
00:05:29,559 --> 00:05:30,720
You're both brave and clever.

65
00:05:31,040 --> 00:05:32,040
Other than the Tang Sect,

66
00:05:32,200 --> 00:05:34,160
where else could there be such outstanding talent?

67
00:05:35,000 --> 00:05:36,000
Talent.

68
00:05:36,600 --> 00:05:37,880
I've been investigating you all this time.

69
00:05:38,160 --> 00:05:39,279
