81
00:05:58,079 --> 00:05:58,559
Mm.

82
00:05:59,040 --> 00:06:00,600
We are lifelong friends.

83
00:06:01,239 --> 00:06:02,679
Lifelong friends.

84
00:06:27,320 --> 00:06:28,079
Young Master

85
00:06:28,559 --> 00:06:30,119
Sneaking around at the door

86
00:06:30,200 --> 00:06:31,040
