88
00:06:32,320 --> 00:06:33,119
Shh

89
00:06:40,000 --> 00:06:40,799
Young Master

90
00:06:40,839 --> 00:06:41,559
So early in the morning

91
00:06:41,600 --> 00:06:43,640
Can you keep your voice down?

92
