93
00:06:50,079 --> 00:06:50,760
But little did I know

94
00:06:50,959 --> 00:06:52,480
They already knew my identity

95
00:06:52,600 --> 00:06:53,399
What?

96
00:06:53,959 --> 00:06:55,200
Then why didn't they react at all?

97
00:06:55,239 --> 00:06:57,119
Because they never intended to deal with me

98
00:06:58,239 --> 00:06:59,720
The friends chosen by the Young Master

99
00:06:59,880 --> 00:07:00,880
