109
00:07:22,040 --> 00:07:23,160
All these years

110
00:07:23,519 --> 00:07:25,119
I've never considered you a subordinate

111
00:07:26,000 --> 00:07:27,040
If you don't mind

112
00:07:27,359 --> 00:07:29,000
I hope you'll remember

113
00:07:29,600 --> 00:07:31,200
