118
00:07:46,000 --> 00:07:46,760
Alright

119
00:07:46,959 --> 00:07:48,160
I still have a mission to complete

120
00:07:48,959 --> 00:07:50,000
I'll take my leave now

121
00:07:56,320 --> 00:07:58,519
Getting all emotional even after everyone's left

122
00:07:58,640 --> 00:08:00,119
