123
00:08:14,679 --> 00:08:15,640
I

124
00:08:16,079 --> 00:08:17,559
I'm almost fully recovered.

125
00:08:17,679 --> 00:08:19,920
Do I still have to drink such bitter medicine?

126
00:08:20,119 --> 00:08:21,320
Good medicine tastes bitter.

127
00:08:21,359 --> 00:08:22,880
The poison in your body was only suppressed.

128
00:08:22,920 --> 00:08:24,160
It damaged your vitality.

129
00:08:24,359 --> 00:08:25,760
You need to take good care of yourself.

130
00:08:25,839 --> 00:08:27,160
Otherwise, you'll be left with lingering illness.

131
00:08:27,160 --> 00:08:28,320
What will you do when you get old?

132
00:08:28,359 --> 00:08:29,640
