138
00:08:39,200 --> 00:08:40,719
I'm going to the Diancha Office.

139
00:08:40,799 --> 00:08:42,359
to achieve my grand ambitions.

140
00:08:42,440 --> 00:08:43,559
That's true.

141
00:08:44,039 --> 00:08:45,239
At that time,

142
00:08:45,599 --> 00:08:47,440
I'll definitely be married.

143
00:08:48,400 --> 00:08:49,520
I just don't know

144
00:08:49,679 --> 00:08:51,440
