145
00:08:52,200 --> 00:08:54,719
She must be a well-bred lady.

146
00:08:54,840 --> 00:08:56,640
From a scholarly family.

147
00:08:57,679 --> 00:08:58,679
Yes.

148
00:08:59,080 --> 00:09:00,840
