162
00:09:21,559 --> 00:09:23,320
That blow to my chest was like breaking a stone.

163
00:09:23,359 --> 00:09:24,599
You almost knocked me out.

164
00:09:24,640 --> 00:09:25,520
And you still dare to talk back!

165
00:09:32,640 --> 00:09:33,479
I...

166
00:09:34,000 --> 00:09:35,039
Honestly,

167
00:09:35,719 --> 00:09:37,200
when I was unconscious,

168
00:09:38,960 --> 00:09:40,359
I kept hearing

169
00:09:40,880 --> 00:09:42,919
someone talking to me by the bedside.

170
00:09:43,960 --> 00:09:45,799
