171
00:09:46,840 --> 00:09:47,960
to give me medicine.

172
00:09:48,559 --> 00:09:49,520
Was that you?

173
00:10:05,679 --> 00:10:06,640
The medicine has already cooled down.

174
00:10:06,679 --> 00:10:07,799
You should take it quickly.

175
00:10:16,559 --> 00:10:17,599
Take your medicine.

176
00:10:17,880 --> 00:10:18,719
Alright.

177
00:10:19,119 --> 00:10:20,119
I have one condition.

178
00:10:20,960 --> 00:10:22,200
I want to eat candied hawthorn.

179
00:10:22,359 --> 00:10:23,080
Tch.

180
00:10:23,239 --> 00:10:24,640
Still acting like a child.

181
00:10:26,239 --> 00:10:27,679
I'll go buy it for you right now.

182
00:10:47,280 --> 00:10:48,280
Since you're here,

183
00:10:49,479 --> 00:10:50,320
come in.

184
00:11:05,440 --> 00:11:07,640
I know you've never liked taking medicine since you were little.

185
00:11:07,919 --> 00:11:10,400
Every time, I would use sweet rice cakes to coax you into taking it.

186
00:11:11,400 --> 00:11:12,400
So,

187
00:11:13,239 --> 00:11:15,520
I specially bought sweet rice cakes and brought them to you.

188
00:11:16,200 --> 00:11:17,599
If you weren't poisoned,

189
00:11:18,159 --> 00:11:19,239
