190
00:11:20,159 --> 00:11:21,159
Fei Ying, I...

191
00:11:22,280 --> 00:11:24,239
I didn't mean to hurt you.

192
00:11:24,520 --> 00:11:25,119
I just...

193
00:11:25,159 --> 00:11:26,840
