200
00:11:48,520 --> 00:11:50,559
What exactly happened seven years ago?

201
00:11:51,239 --> 00:11:52,479
It's been so many years.

202
00:11:52,640 --> 00:11:54,280
I've been waiting for you all this time.

203
00:11:55,760 --> 00:11:57,159
Is this the result of my waiting?

204
00:11:57,239 --> 00:11:58,359
You don't need to wait for me.

205
00:11:59,159 --> 00:12:00,159
I once

206
00:12:01,440 --> 00:12:02,799
wanted to find out the truth too.

207
00:12:04,119 --> 00:12:05,359
Because of that,

208
00:12:05,960 --> 00:12:07,359
I even hurt Linlang.

209
00:12:08,080 --> 00:12:09,400
I've figured it out now.

210
00:12:09,599 --> 00:12:10,840
At this very moment,

211
00:12:11,080 --> 00:12:12,239
I'm very happy.

212
00:12:12,880 --> 00:12:14,000
The past

213
00:12:14,640 --> 00:12:15,919
