214
00:12:17,520 --> 00:12:18,239
No.

215
00:12:19,239 --> 00:12:21,440
I must find out the truth.

216
00:12:22,000 --> 00:12:24,000
I need to give myself an answer.

217
00:12:49,760 --> 00:12:50,840
Come, Linlang.

218
00:13:12,359 --> 00:13:13,599
Can you eat properly?

219
00:13:14,960 --> 00:13:15,960
