220
00:13:16,080 --> 00:13:17,359
My great strategist Sima.

221
00:13:17,760 --> 00:13:18,359
Yes.

222
00:13:18,440 --> 00:13:20,359
Isn't everyone just eating?

223
00:13:20,760 --> 00:13:21,760
Let's be serious.

224
00:13:22,200 --> 00:13:23,239
These past few days,

225
00:13:23,640 --> 00:13:24,760
I personally escorted those who were kidnapped

226
00:13:24,799 --> 00:13:25,960
back to their homes one by one.

227
00:13:26,599 --> 00:13:28,400
I took the opportunity to investigate the population of Mist Town.

228
00:13:29,000 --> 00:13:31,159
I didn't find any families with the surname Xu.

229
00:13:31,679 --> 00:13:32,239
Linlang,

230
00:13:32,719 --> 00:13:34,320
