231
00:13:34,440 --> 00:13:35,840
Father only said that once I arrived in Mist Town,

232
00:13:35,960 --> 00:13:37,400
my uncle would come to find me.

233
00:13:37,799 --> 00:13:39,520
But I've been in Mist Town for so long,

234
00:13:39,840 --> 00:13:41,239
and there's still no news of my uncle.

235
00:13:41,799 --> 00:13:42,719
My older brother is the same.

236
00:13:42,840 --> 00:13:43,559
No trace of him.

237
00:13:43,640 --> 00:13:44,520
The previous clues

238
00:13:44,640 --> 00:13:45,679
pointed to Mist Town.

239
00:13:45,760 --> 00:13:46,960
I originally wanted to uncover

240
00:13:47,039 --> 00:13:48,320
the truth behind the murder in my family.

241
00:13:48,400 --> 00:13:49,080
I didn't expect

242
00:13:49,159 --> 00:13:50,520
it would lead to so many other things.

243
00:13:51,520 --> 00:13:52,159
Now,

244
00:13:52,359 --> 00:13:53,760
thanks to Lord Geng's help,

245
00:13:54,320 --> 00:13:55,840
we were able to take down that group of traffickers.

246
00:13:56,760 --> 00:13:58,719
But I think this is far from over.

247
00:13:59,119 --> 00:14:00,200
What do you think?

248
00:14:01,000 --> 00:14:01,919
As far as I know,

249
00:14:02,080 --> 00:14:03,280
Tianluo and Tang Clan

250
00:14:03,400 --> 00:14:04,880
have both used drugged people for their operations.

251
00:14:05,039 --> 00:14:06,159
The leader of the traffickers

252
00:14:06,440 --> 00:14:08,359
also cooperated with Ye Mei because she was from Tianluo.

253
00:14:08,359 --> 00:14:09,320
and worked with her.

254
00:14:09,400 --> 00:14:11,159
This place belongs to Gushan.

255
00:14:11,239 --> 00:14:12,159
So I think

256
00:14:12,679 --> 00:14:13,440
Gushan

257
00:14:13,520 --> 00:14:15,320
