258
00:14:15,400 --> 00:14:16,359
That makes sense.

259
00:14:17,200 --> 00:14:19,239
After settling the people who were kidnapped by traffickers,

260
00:14:19,520 --> 00:14:20,960
we'll head to Gushan.

261
00:14:21,200 --> 00:14:22,200
to investigate.

262
00:14:22,719 --> 00:14:23,239
Hmm.

263
00:14:23,440 --> 00:14:25,280
But the person in charge of Gushan is very mysterious.

264
00:14:25,320 --> 00:14:27,200
All we know is that their nickname is "Washerwoman."

265
00:14:27,320 --> 00:14:29,039
Very few have seen their true face.

266
00:14:29,440 --> 00:14:31,000
Washerwoman.

267
00:14:31,080 --> 00:14:31,960
Such a formidable person

268
00:14:31,960 --> 00:14:33,559
is actually an elderly woman.

269
00:14:35,239 --> 00:14:36,520
To be able to control Gushan

270
00:14:36,599 --> 00:14:38,719
and lead the most ruthless people in the martial world,

271
00:14:38,919 --> 00:14:40,080
she must be highly skilled in martial arts

272
00:14:40,159 --> 00:14:41,440
and physically strong.

273
00:14:41,919 --> 00:14:43,400
If she really is an old woman,

274
00:14:44,359 --> 00:14:45,599
I'd like to meet her.

275
00:14:45,880 --> 00:14:46,880
You're interested in other women,

276
00:14:47,000 --> 00:14:48,359
no matter if they're old or young,

277
00:14:48,440 --> 00:14:50,239
but you're always picky with me.

278
00:14:50,719 --> 00:14:51,440
These past two days,

279
00:14:51,559 --> 00:14:53,280
why have you been so hostile toward me?

280
00:14:54,919 --> 00:14:55,960
You blockhead,

281
00:14:56,039 --> 00:14:57,359
even if I told you, you wouldn't understand.

282
00:15:01,359 --> 00:15:03,559
What does she mean by that?

283
00:15:04,719 --> 00:15:05,640
Master Geng,

284
00:15:06,000 --> 00:15:07,039
about this matter,

285
00:15:07,239 --> 00:15:08,599
I can't explain it clearly to you either.

286
00:15:08,760 --> 00:15:10,280
